      "reasoning_chain_field": "reasoning",
      "reasoning_chain": "【解】如力图7.24.1所示，取三球连线为$x$轴，设某时刻$t$三球偏离平衡位置的位移为$x_1,x_2,x_3$，运动方程为\n$$\n\\begin{cases} \nm\\ddot{x}_1 = k(x_2 - x_1) \\\\\nM\\ddot{x}_2 = k(x_1 - 2x_2 + x_3) \\\\\nm\\ddot{x}_3 = -k(x_3 - x_2)\n\\end{cases}\n$$\n\n设简谐振动解：\n$$\nx_i = A_i\\cos\\omega t \\quad (i=1,2,3)\n$$\n代入得振幅方程：\n$$\n\\begin{cases}\n(k-m\\omega^2)A_1 - kA_2 = 0 \\\\\n-kA_1 + (2k-M\\omega^2)A_2 - kA_3 = 0 \\\\\n-kA_2 + (k-m\\omega^2)A_3 = 0\n\\end{cases}\n$$\n\n特征频率满足：\n$$\n\\begin{vmatrix}\nk-m\\omega^2 & -k & 0 \\\\\n-k & 2k-M\\omega^2 & -k \\\\ \n0 & -k & k-m\\omega^2\n\\end{vmatrix} = 0\n$$\n\n解得特征频率：\n$$\n\\omega = 0,\\ \\sqrt{\\frac{k}{m}},\\ \\sqrt{\\frac{M+2m}{Mm}k}\n$$\n其中$\\omega=0$为平移解，舍去。\n\n振动模式分析：\n\n1. 当$\\omega_1=\\sqrt{\\dfrac{k}{m}}$时：\n$$\nA_2 = 0,\\quad A_1 = -A_3\n$$\n（$M$球静止，两侧$m$球反相振动）\n\n2. 当$\\omega_2=\\sqrt{\\dfrac{M+2m}{Mm}k}$时：\n$$\nA_1 = A_3,\\quad A_2 = -\\dfrac{2m}{M}A_3\n$$\n（两侧$m$球同相振动，$M$球反相振动）\n\n振动模式示意图见力图7.24.2。",
      "has_reasoning_chain": true
    },
